A fun and fast shooting game!
You control a player, shoot enemies, and survive as long as you can. 

## Features

Easy and smooth player movement
Mouse aiming (the gun follows your mouse)
Colorful enemies that chase you
Cool explosion effects when enemies die
Beautiful star background
Power-ups that give you special abilities
Health bar to show your remaining health
Score increases when you kill enemies
Game becomes harder over time (more enemies)

## Requirements

Python 3
Pygame 

## Installation

1. Make sure you have Python installed on your computer
2. Install Pygame by running:
```
pip install pygame
```

## How to Play

1. Run the game with:
```
python shooter_game.py
```

2. Controls:

   W A S D or Arrow Keys → Move
   Mouse → Aim
   Left Mouse Button → Shoot 
   SPACE → Start / Restart
   ESC → Quit game

3. Gameplay:
   You are a blue circle with a gun
   Enemies come from all sides
   Shoot them before they reach You 
   If an enemy touches you → you lose health
   Game ends when health = 0
   Killing enemies increases your score

## Game Mechanics

   Enemies spawn from the screen edges
   Big enemies need more shots and give more points
   Bullets disappear after some distance
   When enemies die → small explosion particles appear

##Power-ups appear randomly:

   Health (Green Cross) → +50 health
   Speed (Cyan Triangle) → Move faster
   Rapid Fire (Yellow Star) → Shoot faster
   Damage (Red Diamond) → Bullets hit harder

## Tips

   Always keep moving
   Try to shoot enemies that are closest
   Collect power-ups quickly
   Damage boost is very powerful
   Speed boost helps in escaping and collecting items
   Don’t let enemies surround You

Enjoy the game!
